{"title":"马克思头像","authors":["钱叶用"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":5,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思头像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钱叶用"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂着思想者的头颅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是一位导师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位长者的面孔和胡须"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我读导师的传略与诗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛看到高加索悬崖的铁链"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒放着芬芳的鲜花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个后来者，导师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从你的著作中感应着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨大的智慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两颗亮星升起在我头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是你的瞳孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笼罩在河流的波涛上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的船在世界周游闯荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把历史的码头跑遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于见到你用巨斧凿出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类温暖的湾港"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我沉默不语，导师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你生命的密码"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的血液中闪烁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我的全部智慧一起闪烁"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}